{"tid":2008171,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊嚟下睇其他平行時空嘅中共會點處理嚟緊立法會","createTime":"2020-05-08T23:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T06:20:51.000Z","uid":51346,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a5cc3cdf86cdd3fe870f104a226fcc38a96757","tid":2008171,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T23:58:33.000Z","msg":"平行時空1 <br />\n對建制有信心 乜都唔做 最後出嚟嘅選舉結果係控制唔到立法會<br />\n逼住出大絕 推翻選舉結果<br />\n<br />\n你們黃絲不滿建制 是不是?<br />\n你們藍絲不滿泛民 是不是?<br />\n<br />\n好 咱們中國最着重民主 重新選<br />\n<br />\n立法會現時共有70名議員，其中35名經地方選區直接選舉產生，其餘35名由功能界別選舉 產生。 <br />\n<br />\n將改為<br />\n<br />\n新增1名 合共71位立法會議員 比以往更有代表性 <br />\n<br />\n71名議員皆由全中國人民選出 人選並包含香港 保證中立 不會偏袒任何一方<br />\n<br />\n有人質疑唔合基本法 就釋法釋到合為止<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n2022年正式取消五十年不變<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平行時空2<br />\n未選前已dq所有泛民議員 為讓市民感受民主 中共將會貼心安排每個選區/議席皆有一名建制派和保皇派參選 讓市民有選擇的權利<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港豬 仲瞓覺呀?"},{"pid":"952c397f3521141e2fba3b2fef4d0905b8d82e1a","tid":2008171,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3586cd186e817cfdcf8f6ad75202ecc3492266e0","tid":2008171,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3a8035f3ee1418dca426ebd23b301559a18560","tid":2008171,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfeb5f74194f37caf76ea2e67fcbbe9dd87874e","tid":2008171,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b736f44545a31a8a1d0c149d4aa4495590f68312","tid":2008171,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"